NOTE ON vChewing INTEGRATION

TypeLingo is designed to be integrated into an open-source Swift input method
such as vChewing (https://github.com/vChewing/vChewing-macOS), which is licensed
under the MIT-NTL (MIT No-Trademark) License. TypeLingo is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or a product of The vChewing Project, and does NOT use the
"vChewing" / "威注音" name or trademark. When you build a derivative input method
using these integration instructions, you must comply with vChewing's license
and must not distribute it under the vChewing name/trademark.
